# Walkthrough: Fase 0 ‚Äî Selesai ‚úÖ
**FO Testing & Commissioning Desktop App**

---

## Yang Sudah Dibuat

### 1. Laravel Migrations (OpenAccess DB)
3 tabel baru berhasil dibuat dan di-migrate ke MySQL OpenAccess:

| Tabel | Keterangan |
|-------|-----------|
| `fo_test_customers` | Data pelanggan (customer_number, nama, alamat, paket Mbps) |
| `fo_test_sessions` | Sesi pengujian (certification_id, FK ke users + customers, status PASS/FAIL/PARTIAL) |
| `fo_test_results` | Hasil per-test dalam JSON (test_type, target, result_data, status) |

