### 3. NuGet Packages Dikonfigurasi
- `MySqlConnector` ‚Äî koneksi ke MySQL OpenAccess
- `BCrypt.Net-Next` ‚Äî verifikasi password hash (12 rounds sesuai OpenAccess)
- `QuestPDF` ‚Äî generasi PDF (Sprint 3)
- `CommunityToolkit.Mvvm` ‚Äî MVVM pattern
- `MaterialDesignThemes` ‚Äî UI blue theme (#1E5AA0)
- `Serilog` + `Serilog.Sinks.File` ‚Äî logging

---

## Cara Buka & Build di Windows

1. Clone/copy folder `jinom-testing/FoTestingApp/` ke Windows
2. Buka `FoTestingApp.csproj` di **Visual Studio 2022**
3. Visual Studio akan restore NuGet packages otomatis
4. Update `appsettings.json` sesuai environment (host/port DB MySQL)
5. Tekan **F5** atau **Ctrl+F5** untuk build dan run

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Update `appsettings.json` dengan koneksi DB yang benar sebelum build:
> - `Database.Host` ‚Äî IP server MySQL OpenAccess
> - `Database.Port` ‚Äî port MySQL (default OpenAccess: 3311)
> - `Database.Username` / `Database.Password` ‚Äî credential DB

---

## Alur Kerja Saat Dijalankan

1. `App.xaml.cs` ‚Üí inisialisasi Serilog + ConfigManager ‚Üí buka `LoginWindow`
2. User input email + password ‚Üí `AuthService.LoginAsync()` ‚Üí query `users` table ‚Üí BCrypt verify
3. Login berhasil ‚Üí `MainShell` terbuka (sidebar aktif, info user tampil di kiri)
4. Klik **Pengujian Baru** ‚Üí `NewTestPage` ‚Üí isi form pelanggan ‚Üí klik **Mulai Test**
5. `NewTestPage` ‚Üí upsert customer ‚Üí buat sesi ‚Üí jalankan `NetworkTestService.RunAllAsync()`
6. Test berjalan berurutan (Ping GW ‚Üí Ping DNS ‚Üí NSLookup x2 ‚Üí Ping Lokal ‚Üí App Test ‚Üí Speedtest)
7. Setiap test: simpan ke `fo_test_results` + render card real-time di UI
8. Selesai ‚Üí update `fo_test_sessions.overall_status` ‚Üí tombol **Simpan & Cetak Laporan** aktif
9. Klik laporan ‚Üí `ReportPage` (PDF belum selesai, Sprint 3)

---

